l%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191113%2F60261343&h=c6ac7139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191113/60261343</a><br />\n昨天首次停曬八大，之後就暴力清場，好明顯政府認為滅左你大學生，事件就會完，<br />\n所有其它大學要作最壞打算，準備可以立即徹離，唔可以比人圍困 ,大學最重要的係學生，唔係學校<br />\n對無人性的林鄭來說，唔好誤以為停課係為你地安全着想，佢係想暴力清場。<br />\n仲有，有消息內地生徹走，好明顯為屠殺鋪路<br />\n必須推上國際，要話比世界聽&ldquo;天安門事件&rdquo;又即將發生，仲要係警察想走入八大，消滅整個世代的大學生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712238</a>"},{"pid":"1f412b1a9272706b12bbea5976e87bcf582df4e2","tid":1715411,"uid":256383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:53:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d16a867988b8061e79b9f67a8f4cf20f05bef445","tid":1715411,"uid":256383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"846d98cd25985f88bf44b6ee25010408faa91855","tid":1715411,"uid":210087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:53:28.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"0fc4ba4bc517c9677936fe541409367cb6754a1d","tid":1715411,"uid":256383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:54:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f9942e7520e502883488f95a94298b210c75db1","tid":1715411,"uid":210087,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wneOP1h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwneOP1h.png&h=25856c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390849\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390849</a>"},{"pid":"4e886b18252ccfef7981f5d0727ceac7d526ee59","tid":1715411,"uid":256383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:57:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"924057e250bf41d2b8f7c8e117a1f0a9f290e538","tid":1715411,"uid":256383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:59:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19afb5bba06ec46c901dabb0994a2e